    <title type="display">Currency Reform for Fair Trade Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="amended by house">To amend title VII of the Tariff Act of 1930 to clarify that countervailing duties may be imposed to address subsidies relating to a fundamentally undervalued currency of any foreign country.</title>
